# Session Logging

Maintain logs in `quality_reports/session_logs/` for substantive tasks.

## Log at Three Moments

1. After plan approval
2. After each major module milestone
3. At the end of the session

## Minimum Contents

- current goal
- files changed
- verification completed
- open blockers
- next action

Use `templates/session-log.md` when creating a new log.
